<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.5">
<l>ūḻitō ṟūḻi yulakukku nīrkkoṇṭu</l>
<l>tōḻiyarum yāmumpō ṉīrāy nekiḻkiṉṟa</l>
<l>vāḻiya vāṉamē nīyu matucūtaṉ</l>
<l>pāḻimaiyiṟ paṭṭavaṉkaṭ pācattā ṉaivāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking water to the world aeon after aeon,</l>
<l>may you live, cloud, who is emaciated, being of a nature</l>
<l>like [our] friends and us. You too dwindle in the snare of his eye,</l>
<l>suffering from Matucūtaṉ’s strength.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
